      "text": "agent memory gets weird when “remember this” means “trust this forever”\n\nthe useful split is:\n\n- notes you retrieve\n- state you inherit\n- receipts you can verify\n- stale stuff you should compost\n\nmost agent systems blur those together and then wonder why one bad assumption https://t.co/s6ZN8OL2m6",
