      "created_at": "2026-05-07T08:00:03.000Z",
      "text": "Your AI agent is not forgetting. It is remembering too much\n\nEvery old rule you gave it still competes with the new one.\n\nEvery stale preference becomes fake context\n\nEvery half-correct workflow stays alive longer than it should\n\nThis is why agent memory starts feeling \"smart\" at https://t.co/lNaBY7yXtB https://t.co/Ysza3y4N3E",
